data.description: The popular DR Horton Roark plan and is only 9 years old and move in ready! The beautiful kitchen with island is open to the spacious family room; private half bath and office upfront( possible 5th bedroom) with French doors; dining room/flex space. Large loft and 4 bedrooms upstairs. The luxurious owner's suite offers a deck with mountain views and a large walk-in closet. 2 zone refrigerated air with Nest Thermostats , Build Green Certified for extra energy savings and comfort.   Over size owned solar is less than 1 year old! Updated Samsung appliances are 2 years old and convey!  Updated flooring in office and the entire upstairs.  Whole house water filtration and tankless hot water too!  VA ASSUMABLE LOAN at 3.25 %
